  <brief_title>Effects of &quot;Music for the Mind&quot; on Pre-operative Anxiety in Dentistry</brief_title>
  <official_title>a Randomized Controlled Clinical Trial on the Effects of &quot;Music for the Mind&quot; on Pre-operative Anxiety in Dentistry</official_title>
  <sponsors>
